@0 = ~I'm just a simple grocery merchant. I don't think you are interested.~
@1 = ~Where can I buy the goods I need?~
@2 = ~I'm looking for the the town hall, can you tell me where it is?~
@3 = ~Okay, I'll move on then.~
@4 = ~In the Cracked Anvil, of course. Haljal has everything a hero like you might need. In addition, there are many street vendors in Port Llast, one of them even sells scrolls for magicians. Such a strange guy, I'm afraid of him.~
@5 = ~The town hall is west near the city wall. They say Lady Aribeth herself came to see our mayor, probably she is there now.~
@6 = ~Have a good time in Port Llast. Goodbye.~
